PREAMBLE
=============================================================================

This license governs the use, modification, and distribution of web scraping
software and tools. It is designed with two fundamental principles:

  1. Web scraping TOOLS should be free, open, and accessible to everyone.
  2. Web scraping does NOT create ownership of the scraped CONTENT.

Version 2.1 expands on v2.0 with clearer AI/ML training provisions,
stronger protections for original content creators, explicit data retention
and deletion obligations, and improved international compatibility.

This license applies to the Software (code, documentation, configuration
files, build scripts, and associated assets) distributed alongside this
license text. It does NOT apply to any content collected using the Software.

